text: Kenan Stacy Thompson (born May 10, 1978) is an American actor and comedian. He is known for his work as a cast member of NBC's Saturday Night Live (2003-present). He is the show's longest running cast member, as he is currently in his 20th season. ==References== ==Other websites== * * *Kenan Thompson at the Notable Names Database Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Atlanta Category:African-American actors Category:African-American comedians Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Comedians from Atlanta
